Belthassan: Daemos, I think it is time for a meeting of the troops.

Daemos: Mmmm... Perhaps you are right. But you know Gesper is afar...

Belthassan: I think we have to establish our reputation while things 
seem to be calm. We have to act and achieve our goals if we want to 
oppose the Infecticons.

Daemos: Wise analysis... All tripredacus units, this is commander 
Daemos. We will meet in 3 megacycles for troop review and objectives 
definition. This also means you, Strika and Jetstorm!

OOC: Tankor, if you want them back, take them, but be sure to miss the 
least msgs as you can.
